    "We used the glm function in R to fit the model y i ∼ x i + N i + F i, with parameter family = binomial set to a logistic regression.",
    "Regression summaries were obtained using the summ function from the jtools package in R, with parameters scale=T to standardize the regression coefficients by scaling and mean-centering input data, and confint=T to obtain 95% confidence intervals.",
